Hamilton College in Clinton received bomb threat and threat of shooting at 9.45 am .
Students and staff were urged to shelter in place , lock doors , draw curtains and stay away from windows .
Suspicious package found in Kirner-Johnson Building ; bomb squad arrived from Albany to investigate .
A state trooper announced just before 12.40 pm there was no active shooter .
All classes at Hamilton were canceled for the day .
Suspicious package at Kirner-Johnson Building was found to be harmless .